 是非简并的，则其本征函数 
\begin_inset Formula $\phi(\vec{r})$
\end_inset

 有确定的宇称，即
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\phi(-\vec{r})=c\phi(\vec{r})\qquad\exists c\in\left\{ -1,+1\right\} 
\]

